Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on March 07, 2021 Description from Terminal Escape:
The brutality is the simplicity. The first song utilizes five chords. Total. And ORIGEN don't branch out much from there...it's like getting punched in the eye. Repeatedly. And you know the blows are still coming but you just tense up and take it. "Nos Escondemos" is a level five dose of punishment. This is all you get.  ORIGEN
